{"tid":532756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［前CIA間諜案］FBI曾博一鋪放返香港　「雙面人」樣貌曝光","createTime":"2018-01-18T06:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T07:13:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"363a31e7424eae4d958bd46254445181936bdb4b","tid":532756,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180118/photo/bkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180118144059\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180118144059&h=7dc92882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擁有香港居民身份的美國中央情報局（CIA）前情報人員李振成（Jerry Chun Shing Lee，音譯），被美方懷疑作「雙面人」，協助中國找出境內美國間諜。報道指，聯邦調查局（FBI）於2013年發現李振成藏有機密資料，但未即時揭發他，反而為了調查更多中方行動細節，而任由他返回香港定居。另外，有傳媒貼出李振成的照片，可見蓄短鬍子的他相貌頗佳。 <br />\n<br />\n「The Value」在周三的報道中，貼出一幅李振成身穿西裝的近照，並引述消息人士形容：「李振成身材魁梧，待人友善，即使有人在拍賣場不守規矩，他總是禮貌回應。」據悉，李振成為佳士得亞洲區保安經理，平日在香港辦公室上班，故不少收藏家和傳媒或曾與他有過一面之緣。 <br />\n<br />\n對於FBI早於2013年調查李振成，但至近日才拘捕及起訴他，外界提出疑問。《紐約時報》報道，FBI探員在2013年，發現李振成行李中有機密資料，但未有即時與他對質。調查人員決定，為免讓中國政府警覺，讓李振成返回香港，與家人定居。FBI藉此繼續監察其行動，希望抽絲剝繭得知中國如何接連揪出及殺死美國間諜，以及李振成是否有予以協助。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，美國當局向美媒承認，暫未能確定中國一連串滅諜行動，是否與李振成的協助有關，現時未有計劃起訴他間諜罪。曾檢視過案情的前官員亦指，目前針對李振成協助中國政府指控的，僅有環境證據，並沒有確鑿證供，甚至有CIA人員認為，FBI太急於揪出被疑為內鬼的美國華人。 <br />\n<br />\n另有報道指，李振成在當地時間周一（15日）早上8時半抵達甘迺迪機場，FBI探員讓他正常辦理入境，至12時半才把他拘捕，當局未解釋原因，但外界猜測是因為探員欲向他問話，不欲打草驚蛇。 <br />\n<br />\n李振成照片來源： <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thevalue.com/articles/cia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thevalue.com%2Farticles%2Fcia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo&d=K57mQQZxUvxwTeepu0IeDGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=6cacaed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thevalue.com/articles/cia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180118/photo/bkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180118144059\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180118144059&h=25d781aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180118/mobile/bkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180118%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001.html&d=K57mQQZxUvxwTeepu0IeDGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=24bb4815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180118/mobile/bkn-20180118100727400-0118_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9670e1b770c956de5c044fa5de00b639c6ff4010","tid":532756,"uid":51978,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"係幾靚仔"},{"pid":"6e728eaaa9623be612d71036c52f42711bf7b7e6","tid":532756,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗樣"},{"pid":"75de75790f6e1c38df0727aefeb00cac0aee6280","tid":532756,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e728eaaa9623be612d71036c52f42711bf7b7e6","tid":532756,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"咁你狗都不如"},{"pid":"d9e6955cd83e2da9c10315f05940a3097a99b624","tid":532756,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:59:46.000Z","msg":"ABC樣都幫中國做野<br />\n收好多錢?"},{"pid":"2f013342d29c4c8b8f2a033b3b478